At the start of each session, or when you need to understand this project:

1. Read `CONTEXT/CONTEXT_MD_SYSTEM_INSTRUCTIONS.md` — this explains the context
   system and contains project-specific guidance.
2. Read `CONTEXT/CONTEXT_TOC.md` — the auto-generated index of all available context.
3. From the TOC, fetch only the resources relevant to the current task.

Do not load all context upfront. Read descriptions in the TOC first, then fetch.
